### SURENA III Humanoid Robot

#### 2016 – 2017

---

<div style="text-align: justify">  SURENA III is the third generation of Iranian Humanoid robot and selected as one of the most advanced
humanoid robots by the IEEE Spectrum magazine. This robot is fully actuated full-size humanoid robot.
During the one year of working as a member of Dynamic and Control group of SURENA III, I had invloved in conducting numerous advanced algorithms for walking, stair, and slope ascending and descending. SURENA III has unveiled to the public 2 years ago.</div>



{{< youtube mR5IThJslkY >}}


---

###  SURENA Mini Humanoid Robot

#### 2016 – 2017

---

<div style="text-align: justify"> We started to develop a low-cost research platform
for universities, that we call this Mini-SURENA humanoid robot. We built 4 prototypes and I was the key
member of Dynamic and Control group of the Mini-SURENA humanoid robot. I conduct many experiments
during past one year on Mini-SURENA robot. The following videos shows a push recovery controller performance that is developed by me and the video that Vice President for Science and Technology  of Iran tests the push recovery  controller in the public unveiling. </div>


{{< youtube 2pPhKCSmwwo >}}



{{< youtube tFH3fFcG814 >}}




{{< youtube U71STMsbwo8 >}}




